ast.name: Draw3D
ast.comment:
FULL INSTRUCTIONS ARE IN THE TUTORIAL.
Tap and swipe to create the illusion of 3D images. This takes a good amount of practice, but once you get it, you can make amazing structures.
THE LEADER BOARD SCORE IS HOW MANY IMAGES YOU SAVED!
Please share your creations by making a screenshot.

app.comment:
Tap and swipe to draw in 3D!

Instructions are included.

The leader board score counts the number of images you saved.

Please post screenshots.
